<h2 class="sectionedit1"><a name="strchr" id="strchr">strchr</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
Syntax:
</p>
<pre class="cpp code cpp">    <span class="co2">#include &lt;cstring&gt;</span>
    <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span><span class="kw3">strchr</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span> <span class="kw4">char</span> <span class="sy2">*</span>str, <span class="kw4">int</span> ch <span class="br0">&#41;</span><span class="sy4">;</span></pre>
<p>
Finds first occurrence of the character <code>ch</code> in the character string <code>str</code>.
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT1 SECTION "strchr" [1-191] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit2"><a name="parameters" id="parameters">Parameters</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

<code>str</code> - character string to perform the search in
</p>

<p>
<code>ch</code> - character to search for
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT2 SECTION "Parameters" [192-298] -->
<h3 class="sectionedit3"><a name="return_value" id="return_value">Return value</a></h3>
<div class="level3">

<p>

pointer to the found character in <code>str</code>, or <code>NULL</code> if no byte found
</p>

</div>
<!-- EDIT3 SECTION "Return value" [299-393] -->
